Package alix.lucene.analysis

Class FrDics

java.lang.Object
alix.lucene.analysis.FrDics
public class FrDics
extends java.lang.Object
Preloaded word List for lucene indexation in HashMap. Efficiency strongly rely on a custom implementation of chars token attribute CharsAtt, with a cached hash code CharsAtt.hashCode() and comparison CharsAtt.compareTo(CharsAtt).
